.TH XIL\-STEM\-LOG "1" "2026\-04\-19" "xil\-pipeline 0.1.8" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xil\-stem\-log
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xil\-stem\-log
[-h] [--logs-dir DIR] [--output PATH] [--since YYYY-MM-DD] [--show]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Parse xil\-pipeline logs into a stem generation chronology CSV.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-logs\-dir\fR \fI\,DIR\/\fR
Directory containing xil_YYYY\-MM\-DD.log files (default: logs/)

.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI\,PATH\/\fR, \fB\-o\fR \fI\,PATH\/\fR
Output CSV path (default: stem_log_report.csv); use \- for stdout

.TP
\fB\-\-since\fR \fI\,YYYY\-MM\-DD\/\fR
Only include log files on or after this date

.TP
\fB\-\-show\fR
Print CSV to stdout (equivalent to \-\-output \-)

